snippet.title: Stranded 100 Hours on a Homemade Raft - Day 3
snippet.description:
Today is day 3 of surviving on a homemade raft for 100 hours. In this episode we got a huge shipment of wood to build a tiny house on our mega raft. We also attempted more fishing with the need for food getting more and more pressing. After today we will have a home and a warm place to sleep outside of the elements. snippet.title: Royal Family Unite at Kate‚Äôs Christmas Carol Service
snippet.description:
Members of the Royal Family gathered together at Westminster Abbey on Thursday to attend the charity Christmas carol service organised by the Princess of Wales.

King Charles and Camilla, the Queen Consort joined William, Catherine, Prince George and Princess Charlotte, along with extended members of the family, for an evening of festive cheer dedicated to the late Queen Elizabeth II. 

#KateMiddleton #TogetherAtChristmas #RoyalFamily 

Report by Daisy Busel.
